title: The Very Best of Hot Tracks #1 (1992)
description:
The Very Best of Hot Tracks - Volume #1 (1992)

This is the first compilation of 12" singles from the vinyl collections of the 80&#039;s - even though this actually came out on CD in 1992.

Many of these singles are no longer available, although Hot Tracks is still in business as a DJ service.

Again - a collectors item without a doubt!
